  <thing id="fSquallBld" name="Squallblood" description="The magic of the winds flows strongly in your magic.\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} Cha 13, able to cast a spell with the [air] descriptor.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} When you use a spell with the [air] descriptor to make a combat maneuver or grant a bonus to CMD, you gain a +4 bonus to the CMB or CMD, as appropriate." compset="Feat" summary="The magic of the winds flows strongly in your magic." uniqueness="useronce">
