  <thing id="spWindTnl1" name="Wind Tunnel" description="You create a path of calm air surrounded by strong winds. You set the path when the spell is cast, it cannot cross itself, and it cannot later be changed or moved. The path is easily traversed by you and your allies, who gain a +4 bonus to Acrobatics, Climb, and Jump checks made to move along the path. Any other creature must make a\nFortitude save, or it expends 5 additional feet of movement for every 5 feet it travels along the path. Creatures on the path gain a +1 bonus to AC and saving throws, and +4 to CMD, from attacks and effects that originate off the path." compset="Spell">
