  <thing id="cSorcSkyB" name="Skyborne" description="Though sorcerers have an elemental air bloodline in the core rules, it focuses on electricity damage and assuming the actual form of an air elemental. It has no spells or abilities that grant control over air or wind.\n\nThe skyborne bloodline represents those who are descended from djinn or follow ancient religions that venerate spirits of air and sky.\n\nBloodline Powers: Command of the air and movement in the sky comes naturally to you, but you hate being confined either\nphysically or by the rules of society." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
