  <thing id="tmAirBrne" name="Airborne Creature" description="Airborne creature is a simple template that can be applied to any corporeal creature, but is most common among aberrations, animals, and magic beasts. Creatures with this template gain a natural fly rate, and treat Fly as a class skill. The fly rate is equal to 20 feet + 10 feet per size category smaller or larger than medium +10 feet for every 4 hit dice (or fraction thereof).\n\nThe CR of an airborne creature is +1 over the base creature, with a minimum CR of 2." compset="Template" uniqueness="unique">
