  <thing id="cAMWindJnt" name="Wind Jaunt" description="At 1st level, you can summon a burst of wind that will lift and carry you a very short distance. As part of the movement you take during a move action, you can fly 15 feet. This counts as 5 feet of ground movement as part of your normal move rate. At the end of this movement if you are not on solid footing, you fall. You may use this power a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Charisma bonus." compset="ClSpecial">
